This report provides a quick view of sales performance across time, regions, customer segments, and product categories.
The report was generated quickly using the Power BI shortcut Ctrl + /, which allows creating visuals by typing column names and chart types instead of manual drag-and-drop.
Key Insights
	Total Sales: 2.30M
	Total Profit: 286.40K
	Consumer segment contributes the highest sales
	West and East regions are top-performing
	Phones and Chairs are the highest-selling sub-categories
	Sales show an overall upward trend from 2018 to 2021
Report Features
	Sales trend by Year and Month
	Sales by Segment, Region, and Sub-Category
	KPI cards for Sales, Profit, Quantity, and Discount
	State-level filtering for interactive analysis
